               <note id="n1">ImplementationGuide.definition.resource.description</note>
             </notes>
        <source>A document containing key images for a patient. It can refer to a DICOM or non-DICOM image. When referring to a DICOM image, the DocumentReference.content.attachment.url should be a WADO-URI. When referring to a non-DICOM image, the DocumentReference.content.attachment.url should be a direct URL to the image.

When the resource represents a DICOM instance it SHALL contain a the SOP Instance UID in the identifier element. When the resource represents a DICOM series it SHALL contain the Series Instance UID in the identifier element.</source>
        <target></target>
